body:
Fulton,

El Gotan wants to know when the `Users` collection was built and last updated.

Can you run this on TEST and PROD?

```javascript
// Count and date range
db.Users.aggregate([
  {
    $group: {
      _id: null,
      count: { $sum: 1 },
      oldest: { $min: "$createdAt" },
      newest: { $max: "$createdAt" },
      oldestUpdate: { $min: "$updatedAt" },
      newestUpdate: { $max: "$updatedAt" }
    }
  }
])

// Also check if any docs have updatedAt
db.Users.find({ updatedAt: { $exists: true } }).count()
```

We're recommending deletion of this collection - need the dates for the ticket.

